# Task Tracker — UI Rules (from Figma)

Figma file: https://www.figma.com/design/KtWp4lbhc1DxWQFLNlcTgN

Two screens extracted:
- `Walkthrough_Screen` (node: 2:2745)
- `Home_Screen` (node: 2:2845)

---

