## Walkthrough Screen

Component: `WalkthroughScreen`

Background: `#fffce3`
Corner radius: 30

Layout:
```
SafeAreaView (bg: #fffce3)
  StatusBar
  DecorativeBackground  ← floating icon elements (position: absolute)
  MainContent
    Title "Plan your Day in Details"
    Subtitle "There are many variations..."
    CTAButton  ← dark circle with arrow-right icon
  HomeIndicator
```

Title styles:
- Text: "Plan your Day in Details"
- fontFamily: Helvetica
- fontWeight: 700
- fontSize: 26
- color: #000000
- textAlign: center
- lineHeight: 36

Subtitle styles:
- fontWeight: 500
- fontSize: 16
- color: #606060
- textAlign: center
- letterSpacing: 0.64

CTA Button:
- Outer circle: border color #b0b0b0, transparent fill, 84x84
- Inner circle: fill #242424, 67x67
- Icon: arrow-right, white, 24x24 centered

