## Home Screen

Component: `HomeScreen`

Background: `#ffffff`
Corner radius: 30

Layout:
```
SafeAreaView (bg: #ffffff)
  StatusBar
  Header
  FilterTabs
  ScrollView
    CategoriesSection
    TaskListSection
  HomeIndicator
```

