## Header

Height: 31px

Elements:
- Left: hamburger menu icon (3 bars, color #c4c4c4, 14x12px)
- Center: "Home" text (Helvetica Bold, 20px, #000000)
- Right: profile avatar circle (31x31, white stroke)

```tsx
<View style={styles.header}>
  <HamburgerIcon />
  <Text style={styles.headerTitle}>Home</Text>
  <ProfileAvatar />
</View>
```

