## Filter Tabs

Component: `FilterTabs`

Container:
- background: #242424
- borderRadius: 100
- width: 307
- height: 60
- padding: 8 (inset)

Active tab pill:
- background: #ffffff
- borderRadius: 100
- height: 43

Active tab text:
- Helvetica Bold, 16px, color: #242424

Inactive tab text:
- Helvetica Bold, 16px, color: #ffffff

Tabs (implement all 3 — required by the assignment spec):
- "All" (maps to filter: 'all')
- "Active" (maps to filter: 'active')
- "Completed" (maps to filter: 'completed')

The Figma design shows 2 tabs. Extend it to 3 to satisfy the All / Active / Completed filter requirement. Style matches the same dark pill container with a white sliding active indicator.

