## Task List Section

Component: `TaskListSection`

Container:
- background: #fafafa
- borderRadius: 45
- width: 375
- padding: horizontal 34

Section header row:
- Left: "Task List" text (Helvetica Bold, 18px, #000000)
- Right: "Add Task" button (#242424 fill, borderRadius 100, 101x43, Helvetica Bold 12px white)

Divider below header:
- height: 1
- color: #d7d7d7 (or transparent, as it has 0 height in design)

"Select All Task" button:
- background: #242424
- borderRadius: 100
- width: 151, height: 43
- text: Helvetica Bold 12px white

Use FlatList for task items. Never map arrays manually.

