## Task Item

Component: `TaskItem`

Dimensions: 307x57px

Structure:
```
Pressable (width: 307, height: 57)
  View BG (Rectangle, bg: #ffffff, borderRadius: 16)
  Row
    Left: icon (24x24) + task title (Helvetica Regular/Medium 16px #000000)
    Right: checkbox/plus icon (24x24)
```

Category icons used in design:
- Message icon (for "Email Check" task)
- 3 User icon (for "Weekly Meeting", "Team Discussion" tasks)

Completed task style:
```ts
textDecorationLine: task.completed ? 'line-through' : 'none',
color: task.completed ? Colors.textMuted : Colors.textPrimary,
```

Checkbox (right side):
- Shows Plus icon when incomplete
- Shows checkmark/filled icon when complete

