## Empty State

Component: `EmptyState`

Show when `tasks.length === 0` for the current filter.

Text:
- Primary: "No tasks yet" (Helvetica Bold, 16px)
- Secondary: "Add your first task" (Helvetica Regular, 13px, #757575)

